1
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:02,480
According to Guan Sinian's statement,

2
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:05,280
it was indeed for Guan Sinian

3
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:07,040
that Gao Xiaowen killed Yan Wenjun back then.

4
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:09,360
But why would Qin Xiaowan do this?

5
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:12,280
She let the killer go first,

6
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:14,850
then reported it to the police.

7
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,400
Because she knew

8
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:19,160
that given the victim's prestige,

9
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:20,080
his family

10
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:21,280
would never admit

11
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:23,210
the fact that he raped Guan Sinian.

12
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,080
By then,

13
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:27,120
the victim's family will hold Lianxi Tower responsible.

14
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,800
She has to shift all the blame

15
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:29,880
onto Gao Xiaowen

16
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:32,039
to keep Lianxi Tower out of it.

17
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:34,520
That Madam is really sly.

18
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,280
Exactly.

19
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:39,960
She made Gao Xiaowen a fugitive on purpose.

20
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:44,000
Issuing a wanted order is like admitting guilt.

21
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:46,220
As long as he isn't caught,

22
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:48,160
what she did

23
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,039
will never be known.

24
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,880
What exactly has she done?

25
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,320
Think about it.

26
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:57,080
At Lianxi Tower,

27
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:59,520
how could someone just break in,

28
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:02,560
and have the nerve to rape a girl there?

29
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,520
Without the madam's permission,

30
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:08,560
it'd be hard to even get in the door.

31
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:13,000
So Qin Xiaowan must have seen the murder weapon.

32
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:15,200
She knew from the start

33
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,660
that Gao Xiaowen was back.

34
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:19,240
That's why she called the corpse collector.

35
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:21,680
Because she doesn't want us to catch the killer.

36
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,800
She doesn't want the old case reopened,

37
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,960
doesn't want the case she tried so hard to bury

38
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,120
to be exposed again.

39
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,840
How can someone be so cold-blooded?

40
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:30,480
To her,

41
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:33,010
is business more important than a human life?

42
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,320
If it really is Gao Xiaowen,

43
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,400
then Guan Sinian must have also

44
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:40,040
seen the victim and the murder weapon today.

45
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,760
She must have realized

46
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,400
that Gao Xiaowen is back.

47
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:47,160
But Guan Sinian didn't say a word today.

48
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:49,740
Because she wants to shield Gao Xiaowen.

49
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:51,200
Should we just

50
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:53,120
bring Qin Xiaowan and Guan Sinian

51
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,780
in for questioning right now?

52
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,360
If they wanted to talk,

53
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:58,220
they had plenty of chances today.

54
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:00,570
We need to find another way.

55
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,920
We're closed today.

56
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:24,600
Please come back tomorrow.

57
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:27,600
We are from the Municipal Council Health Department.

58
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:36,280
We received a report from the Central Police Station

59
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:39,280
requiring us to disinfect this entertainment venue.

60
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,520
Any residence that has had contact

61
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,079
or an outbreak of infectious disease,

62
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:44,160
as well as entertainment venues,

63
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,360
must be disinfected.

64
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,120
Come in.

65
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,520
Get up.

66
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,400
Go downstairs.

67
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,800
Get up.

68
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,200
Get up and go downstairs.

69
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,680
Medic,

70
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,600
how much longer will this take? It's late.

71
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:45,260
Open the window in 15 minutes to clear the smoke.

72
00:04:51,280 --> 00:04:53,010
This didn't smoke out any rats.

73
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:55,159
That's strange.

74
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:10,080
This room really needs to be disinfected.

75
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:37,360
Qin Xin.

76
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,880
Why is this bloodstain so dark?

77
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,680
The activity of quicklime

78
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,210
changes the air's pH level.

79
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:47,440
Hemoglobin changes color in strong alkali,

80
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:49,900
so the bloodstain becomes more obvious.

81
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:05,680
Look here.

82
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,760
Why is it there?

83
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:37,580
Gao Xiaowen sure knows how to pick a spot.

84
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,930
Where are the two cleaners?

85
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:07,640
They probably left right after disinfecting.

86
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,600
Lock the door, then.

87
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,920
We won't be using this room anymore.

88
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,060
We're screwed.

89
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:22,040
Now we've become the rats.

90
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,890
There must be another exit.

91
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,320
The girls at Lianxi Tower

92
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:58,360
are different from the common whores outside.

93
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,040
The men who come to Lianxi Tower

94
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:04,240
aren't looking for women to sleep with.

95
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:06,120
What they are missing...

96
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,370
is someone they yearn for day and night

97
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,560
but cannot have.

98
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,960
The harder you are to get,

99
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:16,080
the more they'll rack their brains.

100
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,600
When they see you,

101
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:21,360
they must think of love.

102
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:23,760
I don't understand.

103
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,260
After tomorrow night,

104
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,160
you will understand.

105
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,000
When the guests listen to the opera tomorrow,

106
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,800
only sing "The Peony Pavilion".

107
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:40,010
If they ask for bawdy songs like "Eighteen Touches",

108
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:41,920
say you've never heard of them.

109
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,240
Also.

110
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:47,240
When a guest tries to undress you,

111
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,160
you must say,

112
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:51,420
"Please have pity on me, Sir."

113
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:01,960
The girls at Lianxi Tower,

114
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:04,520
even when being deflowered,

115
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:06,840
must do so with dignity.

116
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:15,880
That is absolute nonsense.

117
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,400
What bullshit love.

118
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,800
Wang Deshun said today

119
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,770
that Yingtao has to serve an old man tomorrow.

120
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:23,240
Let's get her out of here.

121
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:26,200
The priority right now

122
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,250
is for the two of us to get out first.

123
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:30,730
Let's keep looking.

124
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,920
But here's the good news.

125
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:45,700
How is being locked up here good news?

126
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:48,400
We're trying to find a way out.

127
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:51,640
Gao Xiaowen should be trying to find a way back.

128
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,560
We just need to wait for him here.

129
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,840
There's something here.

130
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:20,640
A diary.

131
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,800
Rather than a diary,

132
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:29,120
it's more like a love letter.

133
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:34,690
It only covers four months.

134
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:38,010
The last entry was a few days before the incident.

135
00:12:48,800 --> 00:12:50,400
It's possible that Gao Xiaowen

136
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:51,560
came back four months ago

137
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:53,560
and has been living here ever since.

138
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:10,200
Doesn't it look familiar?

139
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,080
Cherry.

140
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:39,320
God.

141
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:47,650
So you knew Gao Xiaowen was back all along,

142
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:48,500
didn't you?

143
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,320
No wonder.

144
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:55,940
Where would a medic come from in the middle of the night?

145
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,280
So for these past months,

146
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:00,720
you've been bringing him food

147
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:01,440
and covering for him.

148
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:03,370
That's why no one found him, right?

149
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:07,680
He should have lived an upright life.

150
00:14:08,520 --> 00:14:10,450
He became a fugitive because of me.

151
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,880
Since he's back,

152
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,900
how could I turn my back on him?

153
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:15,480
So where is he now?

154
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,160
I want to know, too.

155
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:19,600
After the incident that day,

156
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,040
I haven't seen him since.

157
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:24,000
You saw the body,

158
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:26,530
and you recognized the murder weapon.

159
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:27,840
So you know

160
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,370
Gao Xiaowen killed someone again.

161
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,370
I recognized it.

162
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:34,860
Of course I recognized it.

163
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:42,840
Make way.

164
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:36,780
Then why did he do that?

165
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:39,040
Yingtao is just a child.

166
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,520
If it were you,

167
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:44,050
you wouldn't just stand by, would you?

168
00:15:46,680 --> 00:15:48,240
But what he doesn't know is

169
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:50,610
that no one can save this child.

170
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:53,600
From the day she came back,

171
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:56,440
she could never leave again.

172
00:15:57,920 --> 00:15:58,880
Master Xu,

173
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:02,200
don't give yourself away later.

174
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:03,640
The child is young.

175
00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:07,040
If she gets scared, it'll ruin your mood.

176
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:11,240
Just hurry up.

177
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:13,400
Never mind pretending to be a doctor.

178
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:15,800
If that girl is really as good as they say,

179
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:18,600
even playing the fool

180
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:20,280
would be worth it.

181
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:25,440
Pay the deposit before you see her.

182
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,680
What are you standing there for?

183
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:47,610
Serve Doctor Xu some tea, quickly.

184
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:49,480
Usually,

185
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:51,400
the line of people waiting for Doctor Xu

186
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:53,000
goes all the way to next year.

187
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:53,920
Hurry up.

188
00:16:56,920 --> 00:16:57,560
Just now,

189
00:16:58,560 --> 00:17:00,600
Mama Qin told me everything.

190
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,320
Your father's leg

191
00:17:03,640 --> 00:17:04,700
isn't hard to cure.

192
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:09,180
Can you really cure my father?

193
00:17:09,599 --> 00:17:10,730
Starting tomorrow,

194
00:17:11,119 --> 00:17:12,359
have Mama Qin

195
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:14,819
come pick up the medicine on time.

196
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:15,800
In a month,

197
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,300
he'll be cured.

198
00:17:18,319 --> 00:17:19,640
Thank you, Doctor Xu.

199
00:17:26,359 --> 00:17:27,560
Doctor Xu.

200
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:30,000
Thank you.

201
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:32,520
I'll see you out.

202
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:34,880
Okay.

203
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:42,600
So there is no doctor at all.

204
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:44,540
Qin Xiaowan made it all up.

205
00:17:47,320 --> 00:17:49,580
She doesn't even care about human lives,

206
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:51,680
let alone someone's leg.

207
00:17:52,320 --> 00:17:54,380
When is Yingtao getting eliminated?

208
00:17:57,080 --> 00:17:58,120
Today.

209
00:17:59,400 --> 00:18:01,840
Sir, Yingtao has been eliminated.

210
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:06,240
Wait.

